            "title": "4月期指高开109点报26499点",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;    4月期指高开109点，报26499点；5月期指高开114点，报26399点。</span>\n</div>",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-21 09:17:15",
